article_title: Operation RAV, Free Thinkers, Sioux Falls Tomorrow
article_text:
Sioux Falls, SD

There are more than 75,000 veterans in South Dakota, but not all of them know about the services available to them. Now there's a statewide effort to help raise awareness.

You could have a say in shaping Sioux Falls future. How a city wide volunteer effort hopes to improve quality of life in the city through the Sioux Falls Tomorrow survey.

A recently formed group in Sioux Falls hopes to attract what it calls atheists, feminists, scientists and all those with an open mind.

Learn more about the Sioux Falls Free Thinkers.
